{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the use of paye umbrella companies",
        "additional_details": "The use of paye umbrella companies can lead to an individual paying both the employer's and the employee's National Insurance. We view this as effectively being a double payment, and think this system is corrupt.",
        "background": "Ban the use of paye umbrella companies for all workers as we think it is a scam on British people.",
